column3: Well met, adventurer. My name's Galiena, and I work at the House of Splendors for my aunt Rowena.
Following her successful expansion into Idyllshire and the three city–states, she's decided to bring her operations here to Rhalgr's Reach.
Our presence here serves to aid the recovery effort, creating jobs for refugees and stimulating the economy. With your skills, you would be of great help to us.

And of course, if you have any collectables, I'd be happy to take them off your hands in exchange for scrips. With locations realm-wide, it has never been easier to do business with the House of Splendors!
Well met, adventurer. If you know any able crafters or gatherers, I'd be thankful for an introduction.
In order to undertake this quest, you must be a Disciple of the Hand or the Land of level 60 or above.
